# UCL Web — Frontend Standards

Repo: `ucl-web/` — Unchain Labs marketing site.

## Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|-------|--------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 App Router |
| UI | shadcn/radix + Tailwind CSS 4 |
| i18n | `next-intl` |
| Data | `@tanstack/react-query`, axios |
| CMS | Strapi via `@/lib/strapi`, `@/services/cmsService` |

## Do not

- Use MUI or `mui-frontend` skill
- Add shadcn components outside `src/components/ui/` pattern without matching `components.json`
- Hardcode CMS content that belongs in `ucl-web-cms/`

## CMS integration

- API client: `ucl-web/src/lib/strapi.ts`
- Parsers: `ucl-web/src/services/cmsService.ts`
- Blocks renderer: `@strapi/blocks-react-renderer` for `insight.content`
- Env: `NEXT_PUBLIC_STRAPI_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_STRAPI_API_TOKEN`

## Styling

- Use Tailwind utilities and `cn()` helper
- Reuse shadcn primitives from `src/components/ui/`
- Match existing page layout in `src/app/`

## Verification

```bash
cd ucl-web && pnpm lint && pnpm build
```
